OL,3,CJersey politicians call for 'immediate
OL,4,Csuspension of hostilities' in Gaza
OL,6,Fpoliticians have unanimously supported
OL,7,Fan amendment to call for "an immediate
OL,8,Fsuspension of hostilities" in Gaza
OL,9,Fwith a view to "a permanent ceasefire".
OL,11,FThe amended proposition was passed by
OL,12,F45 votes to zero with no abstentions.
OL,14,FIn the wording agreed by all members
OL,15,Fin the States Chamber, politicians
OL,16,Fexpress their "profound sadness and
OL,17,Fdismay at the extent of loss of
OL,18,Fcivilian lives in Gaza and Israel" and
OL,19,F"condemn the taking of hostages and
OL,20,Fall acts of aggression which violate
OL,21,Finternational law".
