OL,3,CJersey politicians call for 'immediate
OL,4,Csuspension of hostilities' in Gaza
OL,6,FThey ask "that an immediate suspension
OL,7,Fof hostilities should be established
OL,8,Fto enable the unconditional release of
OL,9,Fhostages and those held under unlawful
OL,10,Fdetention, the urgent provision of
OL,11,Fhumanitarian assistance, and a
OL,12,Fpermanent ceasefire".
OL,14,FThe States calls for a diplomatic
OL,15,Fresolution "in order to secure
OL,16,Fstability and a lasting peace in the
OL,17,Fregion, based on a solution which
OL,18,Fprovides justice, freedom from
OL,19,Foccupation, and security for both
OL,20,FIsraelis and Palestinians".
