OL,3,CJersey politicians call for 'immediate
OL,4,Csuspension of hostilities' in Gaza
OL,6,FThey also ask for Jersey's Government
OL,7,Fto express these views to the British
OL,8,FGovernment.
OL,10,FThe initial proposition was brought by
OL,11,FDeputy Montford Tadier with five of
OL,12,Fthe six points listed below
OL,13,Fsuccessfully changed by Deputy Ian
OL,14,FGorst's amendments.
OL,16,FThis included removing the term "two-
OL,17,Fstate solution" that Deputy Gorst says
OL,18,Fhas "been problematic for a number of
OL,19,Fislanders and several States Members".
