OL,6,FThe full approved wording is as
OL,7,Ffollows:
OL,9,FThe States are asked to decide whether
OL,10,Fthey are of opinion -
OL,12,FA. To express their profound sadness
OL,13,Fand dismay at the extent of loss of
OL,14,Fcivilian lives in Gaza and Israel and
OL,15,Fto condemn the taking of hostages and
OL,16,Fall acts of aggression which violate
OL,17,Finternational law and result in death
OL,18,Fand harm to civilians, especially
OL,19,Fwomen and children.
