OL,3,CJersey politicians call for 'immediate
OL,4,Csuspension of hostilities' in Gaza
OL,6,FB. That an immediate suspension of
OL,7,Fhostilities should be established to
OL,8,Fenable the unconditional release of
OL,9,Fhostages and those held under unlawful
OL,10,Fdetention, the urgent provision of
OL,11,Fhumanitarian assistance, and a
OL,12,Fpermanent ceasefire.
OL,14,FC. That international law should be
OL,15,Fadhered to in order to prevent death
OL,16,Fand harm to civilians and damage to
OL,17,Fcivilian infrastructure on a mass
OL,18,Fscale.
